__NAME__ purpose
specify name of table to use as user database
__END__


__NAME__ see also
Database,UserDB
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>table_name</replaceable></arg>
__END__


__NAME__ description
Specify name of the user database.
</para><para>
The default user database name is "<literal>userdb</literal>" and rarely
needs to be changed.
__END__


__NAME__ notes
See &glos-UserDB; glossary entry for complete discussion.
__END__

__NAME__ example: UserDatabase layout
<programlisting>
<xi:include parse='text'  href='../files/userdb/userdatabase.txt'/>
</programlisting>
The database can be downloaded 
<ulink url='files/userdb/userdatabase.txt'>verbatim</ulink>.
__END__

__NAME__ example: Specifying UserDatabase
<programlisting>
Database      userdatabase  userdatabase.txt  TAB
UserDatabase  userdatabase
</programlisting>
__END__

